ch <i>Henri</i>."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Henry Cobham was born about 1180, in Cobham, Kent, England, United Kingdom as the son of Serlo de Cobham. He had at least 3 sons. He died on 1 March 1230, in his hometown, at the age of 51."},"et":{"Abt 1180–1 March 1230":"umbes 1180–1. märts 1230","1180–1230":"1180–1230","1215–1252":"1215–1252","1221–1258":"1221–1258","1223–1265":"1223–1265","1157–1187":"1157–1187","1215":"1215","1258":"1258","1157":"1157","1223":"1223","1 March 1230":"1. märts 1230","1265":"1265","1221":"1221","1187":"1187","1252":"1252","1230":"1230","Abt 1180":"umbes 1180","1180":"1180","Cobham, Kent, England":"Cobham, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1180–1 March 1230":"noin 1180–1. maaliskuuta 1230","1180–1230":"1180–1230","1215–1252":"1215–1252","1221–1258":"1221–1258","1223–1265":"1223–1265","1157–1187":"1157–1187","1215":"1215","1258":"1258","1157":"1157","1223":"1223","1 March 1230":"1. maaliskuuta 1230","1265":"1265","1221":"1221","1187":"1187","1252":"1252","1230":"1230","Abt 1180":"noin 1180","1180":"1180","Cobham, Kent, England":"Cobham, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1180–1 March 1230":"environ 1180–1 mars 1230","1180–1230":"1180–1230","1215–1252":"1215–1252","1221–1258":"1221–1258","1223–1265":"1223–1265","1157–1187":"1157–1187","1215":"1215","1258":"1258","1157":"1157","1223":"1223","1 March 1230":"1 mars 1230","1265":"1265","1221":"1221","1187":"1187","1252":"1252","1230":"1230","Abt 1180":"environ 1180","1180":"1180","Cobham, Kent, England":"Cobham, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Henry Cobham est né environ 1180, à Cobham, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fils de Serlo de Cobham. Il a eu au moins 3 fils. Il est décédé le 1 mars 1230, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 51 ans."},"de":{"Abt 1180–1 March 1230":"um 1180–1. März 1230","1180–1230":"1180–1230","1215–1252":"1215–1252","1221–1258":"1221–1258","1223–1265":"1223–1265","1157–1187":"1157–1187","1215":"1215","1258":"1258","1157":"115